{"tid":656232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵864億夠起10萬伙公屋","createTime":"2018-05-07T05:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T00:41:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"990781094ab56b80275d78187a3d84500288be0e","tid":656232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180507/20383327?_ga=2.34114145.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F20383327%3F_ga%3D2.34114145.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435&d=9wiCCIPEbKP8v7XMGyRO%2BzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d5165db5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F20383327%3F_ga%3D2.34114145.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435&h=d17b61bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180507/20383327?_ga=2.34114145.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月07日 <br />\n<br />\n高鐵864億夠起10萬伙公屋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180507/large/a1101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180507%2Flarge%2Fa1101a.gif&h=a68d4fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西九龍總站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【一地兩檢割地】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】18年前研究的區域快線變為今日的廣深港高鐵香港段，預算130億元但以864.2億元埋單，足夠興建10萬伙公屋；通車日期卻推遲33個月。按前高官鄭汝樺所言，每遲一日通車，香港經濟損失500萬，結果通車前已蝕49.5億元，更留下承建商巨額申索、出租內地口岸區租金等多筆糊塗賬。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n《基本法》被打開缺口，內地執法人員「依法」走進西九執行內地法。200公里時速的鐵輪下，香港失去的或比得到多。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄭啟源　趙雅婷  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180507/large/a1101b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180507%2Flarge%2Fa1101b.gif&h=28024807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n馬時亨指點議員：一地兩檢今「最後一次」審議　 「唔好阻住地球轉」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n通識或被閹　教協轟添煩添亂"},{"pid":"1fd2d06b5cf0e57e84d561f8e8cd5f511c9c6d55","tid":656232,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"三跑,港豬噢加埋呢？"},{"pid":"30219bea2f2f4d4354f335dbee66a07eab94ad58","tid":656232,"uid":118833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"大陸啲玩具嚟"},{"pid":"99a25f5b9140068980a0f603177c60626ba3d958","tid":656232,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1fd2d06b5cf0e57e84d561f8e8cd5f511c9c6d55","tid":656232,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"三跑,港豬噢加埋呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"足夠解決香港醫療,房屋,低收入津貼等社會問題"},{"pid":"d48dc9defafdf9c4fd872d74caedae970104114f","tid":656232,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99a25f5b9140068980a0f603177c60626ba3d958","tid":656232,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1fd2d06b5cf0e57e84d561f8e8cd5f511c9c6d55","tid":656232,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"三跑,港豬噢加埋呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"足夠解決香港醫療,房屋,低收入津貼等社會問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"錯，係唔夠班高官出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5cd462d65aeb77aa63fcd90b88d75d7327754e","tid":656232,"uid":68746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99a25f5b9140068980a0f603177c60626ba3d958","tid":656232,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1fd2d06b5cf0e57e84d561f8e8cd5f511c9c6d55","tid":656232,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"三跑,港豬噢加埋呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"足夠解決香港醫療,房屋,低